 71: 
 72: ## Property Guidelines
 73: 
 74: ### Required vs Recommended
 75: 
 76: Always include required properties, aim for recommended properties:
 77: 
 78: ```python
 79: # Required properties (will fail validation)
 80: doc.set_property("name", "Document Title")
 81: doc.set_property("encodingFormat", "application/pdf")
 82: 
 83: # Recommended properties (improves quality)
 84: doc.add_person("author", "Jane Smith")
 85: doc.set_dates(created=datetime.now())
 86: doc.add_keywords(["topic1", "topic2"])
 87: ```
 88: 
 89: ### URL Best Practices
 90: 
 91: **Always use absolute URLs:**
 92: 
 93: ```python
 94: # Good - Absolute URL
 95: doc.set_property("url", "https://example.com/file.pdf")
 96: 
 97: # Bad - Relative URL
 98: doc.set_property("url", "/files/file.pdf")
 99: 
100: # Good - File URL for local files
101: doc.set_property("url", "file:///path/to/file.pdf")
102: ```
103: 
104: ### Date Formats
105: 
106: Use ISO 8601 format for all dates:
107: 
108: ```python
109: # Good - ISO 8601
110: doc.set_dates(
111:     created=datetime(2024, 1, 15, 10, 30, 0),
112:     published=datetime(2024, 1, 20)
113: )
114: 
115: # Result: "2024-01-15T10:30:00" and "2024-01-20"
116: ```
117: 
118: ### Duration Format
119: 
120: Use ISO 8601 duration format:
121: 
122: ```python
123: # Good examples
124: video.set_property("duration", "PT5M30S")  # 5 minutes 30 seconds
125: video.set_property("duration", "PT1H30M")  # 1 hour 30 minutes
126: audio.set_property("duration", "PT3M45S")  # 3 minutes 45 seconds
127: 
128: # Helper method
129: def seconds_to_iso_duration(seconds: int) -> str:
130:     hours = seconds // 3600
131:     minutes = (seconds % 3600) // 60
132:     secs = seconds % 60
133:     return f"PT{hours}H{minutes}M{secs}S" if hours else f"PT{minutes}M{secs}S"
134: ```
135: 
136: ### Keywords and Tags
137: 
138: Be specific and use consistent terminology:
139: 
140: ```python
141: # Good - Specific, consistent keywords
142: doc.add_keywords([
143:     "machine learning",
144:     "neural networks",
145:     "artificial intelligence"
146: ])
147: 
148: # Bad - Too generic, inconsistent
149: doc.add_keywords([
150:     "ML",  # Use full term
151:     "AI stuff",  # Too vague
152:     "Neural Networks",  # Inconsistent capitalization
153: ])
154: ```
