  1: # Timeline Visualization - Design Documentation
  2: 
  3: ## Overview
  4: 
  5: The timeline interface transforms your file organization session data into a compelling visual narrative, showing the evolution and performance of the system over time.
  6: 
  7: ## Design Philosophy
  8: 
  9: ### Visual Storytelling Principles
 10: 
 11: 1. **Chronological Journey**: Users follow a vertical timeline that reads like a story
 12: 2. **Progressive Disclosure**: Overview cards provide summary, expandable details dive deeper
 13: 3. **Status at a Glance**: Color-coded markers instantly communicate session health
 14: 4. **Comparative Analysis**: Easy comparison between runs shows improvement over time
 15: 
 16: ## Component Architecture
 17: 
 18: ```
 19: Timeline Interface
 20: ├── Header (Sticky)
 21: │   ├── Title & Branding
 22: │   └── Aggregate Statistics (3 key metrics)
 23: ├── Controls Bar
 24: │   ├── View Toggle (Timeline/List/Stats)
 25: │   ├── Zoom Controls
 26: │   └── Comparison Button
 27: ├── Timeline Container
 28: │   ├── Timeline Spine (Vertical gradient line)
 29: │   ├── Session Markers (Interactive points)
 30: │   └── Session Cards (Alternating sides)
 31: └── Modals
 32:     ├── Snapshot Modal (Detailed session view)
 33:     └── Comparison Modal (Side-by-side comparison)
 34: ```
 35: 
 36: ## Visual Design System
 37: 
 38: ### Color Palette
 39: 
 40: Using your existing dark theme with purpose-driven color assignments:
 41: 
 42: | Color | Variable | Usage | Psychology |
 43: |-------|----------|-------|------------|
 44: | ![#667eea](https://via.placeholder.com/15/667eea/000000?text=+) `#667eea` | `--primary` | Primary actions, timeline spine | Trust, reliability |
 45: | ![#764ba2](https://via.placeholder.com/15/764ba2/000000?text=+) `#764ba2` | `--secondary` | Gradients, accents | Creativity, depth |
 46: | ![#f5576c](https://via.placeholder.com/15/f5576c/000000?text=+) `#f5576c` | `--accent` | Important highlights | Energy, attention |
 47: | ![#0f1419](https://via.placeholder.com/15/0f1419/000000?text=+) `#0f1419` | `--dark-bg` | Page background | Professional, focus |
 48: | ![#1a1f2e](https://via.placeholder.com/15/1a1f2e/000000?text=+) `#1a1f2e` | `--dark-surface` | Card backgrounds | Elevation, depth |
 49: | ![#10b981](https://via.placeholder.com/15/10b981/000000?text=+) `#10b981` | `--success` | Success states | Positive, healthy |
 50: | ![#f59e0b](https://via.placeholder.com/15/f59e0b/000000?text=+) `#f59e0b` | `--warning` | Warning states | Caution, attention needed |
 51: | ![#ef4444](https://via.placeholder.com/15/ef4444/000000?text=+) `#ef4444` | `--danger` | Error states | Critical, requires action |
 52: 
 53: ### Typography Scale
 54: 
 55: ```css
 56: Display:     1.75rem (28px) - Modal titles
 57: Heading:     1.5rem  (24px) - Page title
 58: Subheading:  1rem    (16px) - Section titles
 59: Body:        0.875rem (14px) - Main content
 60: Caption:     0.75rem (12px) - Metadata labels
 61: Micro:       0.7rem  (11.2px) - Badges, codes
 62: ```
 63: 
 64: **Font Stack**: `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif`
 65: 
 66: ### Spacing System
 67: 
 68: Based on 0.25rem (4px) increments:
 69: 
 70: ```
 71: xs:  0.25rem (4px)
 72: sm:  0.5rem  (8px)
 73: md:  1rem    (16px)
 74: lg:  1.5rem  (24px)
 75: xl:  2rem    (32px)
 76: 2xl: 3rem    (48px)
 77: ```
 78: 
 79: ### Border Radius
 80: 
 81: ```
 82: Small:   0.5rem  (8px)  - Buttons, metrics
 83: Medium:  0.75rem (12px) - Cards, inputs
 84: Large:   1rem    (16px) - Panels
 85: XLarge:  1.5rem  (24px) - Modals
 86: Pill:    9999px         - Badges, tags
 87: ```
 88: 
 89: ## Key UI Components
 90: 
 91: ### 1. Timeline Spine
 92: 
 93: **Visual Design**:
 94: - 4px wide vertical line
 95: - Gradient from primary (top) to accent (bottom)
 96: - Centered on desktop, left-aligned on mobile
 97: - Glowing effect with box-shadow
 98: 
 99: **Purpose**: Provides visual anchor and chronological continuity
100: 
101: ```css
102: .timeline-spine {
103:     width: 4px;
104:     background: linear-gradient(180deg,
105:         var(--primary) 0%,
106:         var(--timeline-line) 30%,
107:         var(--timeline-line) 70%,
108:         var(--accent) 100%
109:     );
110:     box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--glow-primary);
111: }
112: ```
113: 
114: ### 2. Session Markers
115: 
116: **Visual States**:
117: - **Success** (green): < 10 errors
118: - **Warning** (orange): 10-100 errors
119: - **Error** (red): > 100 errors
120: 
121: **Interaction**:
122: - Hover: Scale up 40%, pulse animation
123: - Click: Opens detailed snapshot modal
124: 
125: **Design Pattern**:
126: ```
127: Resting:  20px circle
128: Hover:    28px circle + pulse effect
129: Active:   Border highlight
130: ```
131: 
132: ### 3. Session Cards
133: 
134: **Layout Pattern**:
135: ```
136: ┌─────────────────────────────────┐
137: │ Header (Date + Badge)           │
138: ├─────────────────────────────────┤
139: │ Metrics Grid (4 columns)        │
140: │ ┌───────┬───────┬───────┬─────┐│
141: │ │ Files │ Org   │ Errors│ Cost││
142: │ └───────┴───────┴───────┴─────┘│
143: ├─────────────────────────────────┤
144: │ Progress Bar (Success Rate)     │
145: ├─────────────────────────────────┤
146: │ Category Tags (Top 4)           │
147: └─────────────────────────────────┘
148: ```
149: 
150: **Alternating Sides**:
151: - Odd items: Right side of timeline
152: - Even items: Left side of timeline
153: - Mobile: All cards aligned to right
154: 
155: **Interaction**:
156: - Hover: Lift effect (-4px translateY)
157: - Click: Opens detailed modal
158: 
159: ### 4. Snapshot Modal
160: 
161: **Structure**:
162: ```
163: ┌───────────────────────────────────────┐
164: │ Header: Title + Close Button         │
165: ├───────────────────────────────────────┤
166: │ Primary Metrics (3x2 grid)           │
167: │ ┌──────────┬──────────┬──────────┐  │
168: │ │ Files    │ Organized│ Skipped  │  │
169: │ │ Errors   │ Duration │ Cost     │  │
170: │ └──────────┴──────────┴──────────┘  │
171: ├───────────────────────────────────────┤
172: │ Derived Metrics (3 columns)          │
173: │ Success Rate | Files/Sec | Cost/File │
174: ├───────────────────────────────────────┤
175: │ Charts Grid (2 columns)              │
176: │ ┌────────────────┬────────────────┐ │
177: │ │ Category Dist  │ Performance    │ │
178: │ │ (Bar chart)    │ (Metrics)      │ │
179: │ └────────────────┴────────────────┘ │
180: └───────────────────────────────────────┘
181: ```
182: 
183: **Animation**: Slide in from top with scale transform
184: 
185: ### 5. Comparison Modal
186: 
187: **Layout**:
188: ```
189: ┌─────────────┐       ┌─────────────┐
190: │  Session 1  │   →   │  Session 2  │
191: │             │  vs   │             │
192: │  Metrics    │       │  Metrics    │
193: │             │       │  + Deltas   │
194: └─────────────┘       └─────────────┘
195:            ↓
196:     ┌─────────────┐
197:     │  Analysis   │
198:     │  Summary    │
199:     └─────────────┘
200: ```
201: 
202: **Delta Indicators**:
203: - Green ↑: Positive change (more organized, fewer errors)
204: - Red ↓: Negative change
205: - Small, monospaced font for precision
206: 
207: ## Animation System
208: 
209: ### Entrance Animations
210: 
211: **Timeline Items**:
212: ```css
213: animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards
214: animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s  /* Stagger */
215: ```
216: 
217: **Modal**:
218: ```css
219: animation: modalSlideIn 0.4s ease
220: /* Slide in from top with scale */
221: ```
