246: ## Data Visualization
247: 
248: ### Progress Bars
249: 
250: **Design**:
251: - Height: 6px
252: - Background: Dark card color
253: - Fill: Linear gradient (primary → accent)
254: - Border radius: 3px
255: - Smooth width transition: 0.6s ease
256: 
257: **Usage**:
258: - Success rate visualization
259: - Category distribution in modal
260: 
261: ### Category Tags
262: 
263: **Design**:
264: - Pill shape (border-radius: 9999px)
265: - Dark card background
266: - Count badge: Primary color, white text
267: - Small font (0.75rem)
268: 
269: **Layout**: Flex wrap with 0.5rem gap
270: 
271: ### Metric Cards
272: 
273: **Structure**:
274: ```
275: ┌─────────────┐
276: │ LABEL       │ ← Small caps, secondary color
277: │ 1,234       │ ← Large, bold, primary color
278: ├─────────────┤
279: │ [Progress]  │ ← Optional progress bar
280: └─────────────┘
281: ```
282: 
283: **Color Coding**:
284: - Default: Primary color
285: - Success metrics: Green
286: - Error metrics: Red (if > threshold)
287: - Cost metrics: White
