289: ## Responsive Design
290: 
291: ### Breakpoints
292: 
293: ```css
294: Desktop:  > 1024px  (Default layout)
295: Tablet:   640-1024px (Adjusted grid)
296: Mobile:   < 640px   (Single column)
297: ```
298: 
299: ### Mobile Adaptations
300: 
301: **Timeline**:
302: - Spine moves to left (20px from edge)
303: - All cards aligned to right of spine
304: - Triangular pointers all point left
305: 
306: **Grids**:
307: - 4-column metrics → 2 columns
308: - Charts grid → Single column
309: 
310: **Header**:
311: - Stats stack vertically
312: - Font sizes reduce 10-15%
313: 
314: **Modals**:
315: - Full-width with padding
