318: ## Accessibility
319: 
320: ### Color Contrast
321: 
322: All text meets WCAG AA standards:
323: - Primary text on dark bg: 13.5:1 ratio
324: - Secondary text on dark bg: 7.2:1 ratio
325: - Buttons have 4.5:1 minimum
