345: ## Performance Optimization
346: 
347: ### CSS
348: 
349: - Hardware-accelerated transforms (translateY, scale)
350: - Will-change hints on animated elements
351: - Efficient selectors (no deep nesting)
352: 
353: ### JavaScript
354: 
355: - Debounced scroll handlers
356: - Lazy loading for large datasets
357: - Virtual scrolling for 100+ sessions
358: 
359: ### Images
360: 
361: - No images required (pure CSS/SVG)
362: - Icon fonts or inline SVG for icons
