169: ### R8 — Add unit tests for scripts/shared/ module
170: 
171: **Status:** Pending
172: 
173: The six files in `scripts/shared/` have no unit test coverage. Existing test fixtures in `tests/conftest.py`
174: (`temp_dir`, `temp_db_path`, `sample_image_file`) would make it trivial to test `resolve_collision`, `get_db_connection`,
175: `db_connection`, and `extract_ocr_text`. Priority: should be added before major refactoring of these utilities.
